Package: blinkdash
Title: Visual Static Reactive Dashboards for GitHub Pages
Version: 0.7.0
Authors@R: person("Alek", "Rutkowski", email = "alek.rutkowski@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A browser-based visual dashboard builder backed by a small localhost R server. It exports static JavaScript dashboards with embedded data, explicit reactive input-output wiring, movable cards, tables, native plots with vector SVG export, markdown, trusted HTML, searchable selectize inputs, YAML source editing, and optional webR processors for browser-side R calculations.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
